---
// NavySection.astro
---

<div
  class="relative bg-cover bg-center text-white bg-black lg:py-12"
  style="background-image: url('/india-map-background.png');">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-60"></div>
  <div
    class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row items-center py-12 px-6 lg:px-16">
    <div class="lg:w-2/3 mt-10 lg:mt-0">
      <h2
        class="hidden lg:block text-xl lg:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">
        Official Solutions Provider: Indian Navy
      </h2>
      <div class="hidden lg:block border-b-4 border-teal-400 w-[50%] mb-4">
      </div>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-justify">
        Our dedication and accomplishments were formally acknowledged when we
        attained the prestigious Indian Navy vendor approval on the 24th of May
        2023. This significant milestone signifies our recognition as a trusted
        and authorized partner, empowering us to serve all four Naval Commands:
      </p>
      <ul class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <li class="mb-2">Western Naval Command - Mumbai</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Eastern Naval Command - Visakhapatnam</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Southern Naval Command - Kochi</li>
        <li class="text-teal-400">Tri-services Command - Port Blair</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-justify">
        This underscores our comprehensive reach and steadfast commitment to
        bolstering the Indian Navy across diverse geographical locations.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2
        class="block lg:hidden text-xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">
        Official Solutions Provider: Indian Navy
      </h2>
      <div class="block lg:hidden border-b-4 border-teal-400 w-[50%] mb-4">
      </div>

      <div class="w-full mt-8 lg:mt-0 flex justify-center">
        <img
          src="/india-map.png"
          alt="Indian Navy Commands"
          class="w-full lg:w-3/4"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
